Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:09.90,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Atrocious Serial Murder Case\NSpecial Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin with the Public Intelligence report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The total number of reports from the public, including phone calls, currently stands at 3029.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the large majority of them seems to be prank calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been 14 reported incidents of people who either know or have seen Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have investigated these thoroughly, one by one, and I believe that - just as reported - it would be safe to say that none of them have any credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are also 21 reported incidents of people claiming to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of those 21 reports has been followed up, and will remain on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving onto the victims..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:03:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can confirm that information on all the known victims that died of heart attacks was publicly available in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, {\alpha&HFF&}we have followed up L's specific request that we investigate the assumed time of death for each victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, we have followed up L's specific request that we investigate the assumed time of death for each victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Results indicate that 68% of all deaths occurred during weekdays, between four in the afternoon and midnight, Japanese time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of deaths peaks over the weekend, when they can occur at any time between eleven in the morning through till late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all extremely interesting information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suggests that given the assumed times of death, {\alpha&HFF&}there is a possibility that our culprit may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suggests that given the assumed times of death, there is a possibility that our culprit may be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have further grounds to support this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they appear to be only targeting criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}the culprit seems to be motivated by a sense of "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they appear to be only targeting criminals, the culprit seems to be motivated by a sense of "justice".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's conceivable that they may even plan on becoming some kind of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we may be dealing with an extremely hollow psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is mere speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}please rid yourselves of any preconceptions you might have that our culprit cannot be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, please rid yourselves of any preconceptions you might have that our culprit cannot be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To consider every possibility; {\alpha&HFF&}that is likely to be the shortest road to apprehending Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To consider every possibility; that is likely to be the shortest road to apprehending Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue the investigation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other observations?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. {\alpha&HFF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to support Kira in any way by saying this.. {\alpha&HFF&}but over the last few days.. throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to support Kira in any way by saying this.. but over the last few days.. {\alpha&HFF&}throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to support Kira in any way by saying this.. but over the last few days.. throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. {\alpha&HFF&}the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to support Kira in any way by saying this.. but over the last few days.. throughout the world, but especially in Japan.. the number of serious crimes committed have dramatically decreased.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.. {\alpha&HFF&}that kind of phenomenon was to be expected..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.. that kind of phenomenon was to be expected..
