Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. L, that concludes today's investigation report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. {\alpha&HFF&}I feel that we're one step closer to finding the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. I feel that we're one step closer to finding the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have another order to trouble you with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the teams investigating victims, information and Internet to double-check what information regarding each victim was previously released in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More specifically, whether or not footage or photographs of the victims had been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks. {\alpha&HFF&}The late nights are beginning to take their toll on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks. The late nights are beginning to take their toll on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about this now, {\alpha&HFF&}everyone was probably already aware of what I said about crime going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about this now, everyone was probably already aware of what I said about crime going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to speak the truth, no matter what kind of truth it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when it's awkward to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:06:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, if everyone continues to think that Kira should be commended for lowering crime, it will become harder and harder to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Surely no one would commend such a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely no one would commend such a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I could count on you, onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. {\alpha&HFF&}Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. Yeah, sort of.
