Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}Why don't you at least try doing the last question yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't you at least try doing the last question yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will. After dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have everything in hand, seeing you're able to afford the time to help out with your sister's homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the police were to come after me, {\alpha&HFF&}I'm confident that I have something to fight them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the police were to come after me, I'm confident that I have something to fight them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, {\alpha&HFF&}father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.. {\alpha&HFF&}Yes, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh.. Yes, I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are your studies going, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always. {\alpha&HFF&}Top of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as always. Top of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my older brother! {\alpha&HFF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my older brother! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my son! {\alpha&HFF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of my son! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem tired, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to say much, {\alpha&HFF&}but this case is proving to be exceedingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to say much, but this case is proving to be exceedingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is part of the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the source of your confidence, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can also access my father's computer without leaving any trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can get hold of all the information regarding the investigation, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:08:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the police are already beginning to suspect that the culprit could be a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that be risky for you, Light?
