Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct, isn't it Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, {\alpha&HFF&}if you write "heart attack" first, you can still write details of their death afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if you write "heart attack" first, you can still write details of their death afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll be able to provide you with some more entertainment, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.75,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Atrocious Serial Murder Case\NSpecial Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}There were another 23 victims yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There were another 23 victims yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were 23 victims the day before that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All spaced out evenly, one every hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that this has continued over two weekdays must mean..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theory that the culprit could be a student is weakened..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone can potentially skip two days of school..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the likelihood of them being a student has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is not what Kira is trying to say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have they spaced the killings at precisely one hour intervals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, {\alpha&HFF&}why are the victims all prisoners that could be found quickly after their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, why are the victims all prisoners that could be found quickly after their deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is trying to tell us.. {\alpha&HFF&}that they can control the time of death at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is trying to tell us.. that they can control the time of death at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility that Kira could be a student was put forward, {\alpha&HFF&}the timing of the murders change to indicate that this was not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the possibility that Kira could be a student was put forward, the timing of the murders change to indicate that this was not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\alpha&HFF&}the timing is too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the timing is too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira must have access to police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly.. {\alpha&HFF&}a direct challenge to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly.. a direct challenge to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that L will probably begin to sweat a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have 50 criminals that I've deliberately left alive for a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, thanks to the last few incidents L should be beginning to suspect someone in, or connected to, the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has a way of getting police information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fact can no longer be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kira's final objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, showing them that you have connections to the police place you at a greater disadvantage than having them suspect Kira of being a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is, {\alpha&HFF&}I did it to help me find and destroy L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is, I did it to help me find and destroy L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are very few people who actually trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even amongst the police force.. {\alpha&HFF&}and especially between the police and L, who never had a bond of trust between them from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even amongst the police force.. and especially between the police and L, who never had a bond of trust between them from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you honestly trust someone whose name and face are unknown to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows that I'm getting police information, {\alpha&HFF&}without a doubt, he'll try to find a trail leading to me that starts within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that L knows that I'm getting police information, without a doubt, he'll try to find a trail leading to me that starts within the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, it'll only be a matter of time before even the police can't keep quiet with respect to L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, {\alpha&HFF&}L and the police appear to be working together to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the outside, L and the police appear to be working together to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, {\alpha&HFF&}L will be investigating the police, and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, L will be investigating the police, {\alpha&HFF&}and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But behind the scenes, L will be investigating the police, and the police will be investigating L!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be the one who'll find L.. {\alpha&HFF&}the police will do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be the one who'll find L.. the police will do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'll erase him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then.. I'll erase him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.53,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Atrocious Serial Murder Case\NSpecial Investigative Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.49,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, {\alpha&HFF&}they are letters of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, they are letters of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we're moved to a different case, {\alpha&HFF&}we're leaving the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we're moved to a different case, we're leaving the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. {\alpha&HFF&}why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we value our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L's theory is that Kira has some ESP-like power that allows them to kill without having to be there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}I'd try to kill those who are trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, I'd try to kill those who are trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if they get caught, they'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already seen this from that incident on TV, {\alpha&HFF&}when Kira killed the "dummy L" after being provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already seen this from that incident on TV, when Kira killed the "dummy L" after being provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But L hasn't even revealed his name, {\alpha&HFF&}let alone his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But L hasn't even revealed his name, let alone his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That order we received earlier from L, {\alpha&HFF&}about checking the information released about the victims prior to their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That order we received earlier from L, about checking the information released about the victims prior to their deaths,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether or not footage or photos of their faces had been released.. {\alpha&HFF&}That turned out to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whether or not footage or photos of their faces had been released.. That turned out to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them had their photo published in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike someone we all know; {\alpha&HFF&}we've had to investigate using our police IDs with out photos attached!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike someone we all know; we've had to investigate using our police IDs with our photos attached!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without hiding our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could be killed by Kira at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're asking to be re-assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}You! Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You! {\alpha&HFF&}Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You! Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to solve this problem we must first establish the concept that x squared equals large X.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can then proceed by noting that the quadratic equation in large X is the key to understanding the problem..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had the FBI arrive in Japan four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've begun their investigation of the Japanese police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the people on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 141 people within the police who have access to information regarding Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people, or people close to them.. {\alpha&HFF&}Kira will definitely be amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But within the 141 people, or people close to them.. Kira will definitely be amongst them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.71,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper contains information about Yagami Souichirou, and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you not to talk to me in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, in that case, I'll just talk at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna listen, just cover your ears or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways I think the notebook was found by an awesome person, {\alpha&HFF&}because I have to remain by your side until either you or that Death Note expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways I think the notebook was found by an awesome person, because I have to remain by your side until either you or that Death Note expires.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm not on your side, and I'm not going to be on L's side either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. I'm not on your side, {\alpha&HFF&}and I'm not going to be on L's side either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. I'm not on your side, and I'm not going to be on L's side either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much already, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll never say that what you're doing is right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although as your roommate, I may have a few things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying things like this now? {\alpha&HFF&}It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying things like this now? It's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore what I'm about to say is not because I'm on Kira's side, {\alpha&HFF&}but because it's giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore what I'm about to say is not because I'm on Kira's side, but because it's giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a human following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been bugging me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, {\alpha&HFF&}but because I'm always following you around, it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, but because I'm always following you around, {\alpha&HFF&}it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I know he can't see me, but because I'm always following you around, it kinda feels like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get rid of him as soon as possible, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that L has already started to suspect the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever is investigating the police must have large resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have 50 people on the case, {\alpha&HFF&}the chances that they'll suspect I'm Kira are non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have 50 people on the case, the chances that they'll suspect I'm Kira are non-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't be looking at me as anything more than a final year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I leave him alone for a few months, {\alpha&HFF&}the probability that I'll be caught might rise above zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I leave him alone for a few months, the probability that I'll be caught might rise above zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I need my stalker's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can figure that out, I can take care of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... {\alpha&HFF&}Let me tell you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... Let me tell you something cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two very important differences between a Shinigami and a human with a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Shinigami write human names into their Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty talkative today, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Shinigami take human life spans for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take their "Life spans"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you take someone due to die at 60, and write their name so they die at 40 instead..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty minus forty, is twenty. {\alpha&HFF&}Those twenty human years are added to that Shinigami's life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sixty minus forty, is twenty. Those twenty human years are added to that Shinigami's life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as we don't slack off too much, {\alpha&HFF&}a Shinigami can't be killed with a bullet to the head, or a knife through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as we don't slack off too much, a Shinigami can't be killed with a bullet to the head, or a knife through the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, {\alpha&HFF&}your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you write a human's name in the Death Note, Light, your life span won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of the differences between a Shinigami and a human with a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a theory about Shinigami that humans haven't heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second difference will probably be even more of an interest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it concerns decreasing life spans rather than increasing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decreasing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami can tell someone's name by just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami's eyes have the ability to see a person's name and life span by just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name and life span?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:21.15,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami Light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I can see your name and life span right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I converted that into human time, you would know precisely how many human years you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we aren't allowed to tell you that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a huge blabbermouth like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, a Shinigami will never be prevented from killing someone due to not knowing their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they kill someone, they know exactly how much life they're gaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our eyes are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the distinct difference between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if a Shinigami drops a notebook, and a human picks it up.. {\alpha&HFF&}the Shinigami can change that human's eyes into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if a Shinigami drops a notebook, and a human picks it up.. the Shinigami can change that human's eyes into the eyes of a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you agree to the deal passed down for this purpose since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for the eyes of a Shinigami is.. {\alpha&HFF&}half of that human's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price for the eyes of a Shinigami is.. half of that human's remaining life span.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of my remaining life span...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, suppose you were to live for another 50 years, that would be reduced to 25 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a year remaining, you get left with half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But currently given that you're not on my side, or on L's side, {\alpha&HFF&}you won't tell me the names of the people I want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But currently given that you're not on my side, or on L's side, you won't tell me the names of the people I want to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you're saying that I can't simply borrow your powers..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. That's one of the rules of the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the price of just half your remaining life span.. {\alpha&HFF&}you could have the eyes of a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the price of just half your remaining life span.. you could have the eyes of a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I'll be able to tell the name of anyone I meet just by looking at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note would become even easier to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. {\alpha&HFF&}What do you want to do, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. What do you want to do, Light?
